<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>힌디어</dt><br>
<dd>the most widely spoken of modern Indic vernaculars; spoken mostly in the north of India; along with English it is the official language of India; usually written in Devanagari script</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Hindi</dd><br>
